reviews.text: Hiukan jäykkä asukkaiden asennoituminen, mutta ystävällinen asenne ihmisillä

Hyvä veneilyyn, huono kaikkeen muuhun.
Älä kalasta kun tulee mädäntynyttä kalaa
Älä ui tai olet vihreän liman peitossa sen jälkeen
Great sport center with a huge variety of activities from long distance ski jumps to soccer.
Competitions are well organized. Big swimming pool and access to the jumping hill at summer, public skiing are most of the winter

Summer: a nice outdoor swimming pool with sauna. Entrance 5.50€ (adult). 
Winter: a winter sports stadium.

Even in summer, this area of Lahti is worth a visit. We wandered around the old(?) ski jumps and you could even climb them to get a better view. The modern ones are closed to visitors it seemed, and also the outlook appeared closed. However, there was a swimming pool open at the base of the big jump. If you are into skiing and nice walks in forests, come here.
Siellä parhaat liikuntareitit, hieno paikka muutenkin .

Trio has a great atmosphere with an awesome staff. We came in for the New Years preset menu which sounded divine! Our first courses were great, however our steak came out over cooked and we were quite bummed. Fortunately the chef came by and asked us how our experience was, and he immediately sent out a new perfectly cooked steak and won us over! The food really is incredible and the chefs do a great job. We will be back and greatly appreciate the customer service!

Though the portions seemed small, the food was very good at Trio. Our server forgot about us a few times (neglecting to bring drinks or check in about the meal), but she was very friendly and knowledgeable. Probably just overworked. The atmosphere was nice, too, though it was exceptionally loud.
Had the fish special. It was great. Grouper asparagus and potatoes. The fish was crisp on the outside and soft on the inside.

We tried this place because the chef of a restaurant in Raleigh, NC we love recommended it. The food was absolutely delicious and the hostess/host were so welcoming and kind. Unfortunately, we had a rude waiter who acted like we were inconveniencing him every time we ordered. He was very short and made a snide comment after we asked for a recommendation on an appetizer and we went for the opposite of his choice. We didn’t pick his recommendation bc he didn’t seem enthused or that he cared what we ordered. This restaurant is in my top 3 favorites while staying in Jackson; just unfortunate we had a negative encounter with a server.
Good food, reasonable price, and it's Jackson hole.
Excellent sliced meat salad!
ok
Super miejsce by smacznie zjeść i się najeść. Porcje nie małe i pyszne. Przyjazna obsługa (choć jest mały problem w porozumieniu w innym języku niz fiński)
Tosi hyvät ja nopeasti tehdyt ruuat

Erinomainen hinta laatu suhde. Annokset runsaita monipuolisia ja maukkaita.
Erinomainen lounaspaikka.

First time here, and most likely will not be back. Food was good however service was lacking. Wait staff was inattentive and never looked past the table he was at to see if others needed assistance. The ground beef has a nearly equal portion of peppers in it, something that is not expected. I love peppers, but not that much! Worth a visit for sure, but not my favorite place to go by any means.

Probably one of the best options for Mexican food in Apple Valley if not the best. Their table side guacamole is excellent and the prices are more than reasonable for what you get. They have also proven themselves very attentive and helpful when we dined there with a larger group. There are cheaper options probably for Mexican fair but you get what you pay for. They also have coupons in the paper fairly often and the fajitas for two is an excellent money saver and honestly is enough food for three or even four people.

We stopped in for a late lunch as this is one of our favorite restaurants. Service is always good but this time we were lucky enough to get Elias D as our waiter. He has to be one of the kindest and most efficient waiters. He had our chips and salsas to the table before we had even settled in. His knowledge of the menu was outstanding and not to mention the guacamole he made for us at our table was awesome. Thanks Elias D for the very enjoyable experience. :)

Decor is lovely! Service was quick and very courteous even during peek hrs on Friday night. The food was fine but I had been hoping for an authentic Mexican place. Here they served ranch along w their mild salsa to go with the (excellent) chips and “nacho cheese sauce” over the chimichangas. Just wasn’t what I had been looking for.

Not sure what happened to this place. Last two times we were here the service has been incredibly slow. Took over 30 minutes to get our food when it wasn't even busy. Food is good but comes out cold. The woman who sat us threw the menus on the table, she also happened to be our waitress. After that it took her approximately 10 minutes to come back to get our drink order. We come here often, but after these last few visits, I'm not sure we will be back.
Great pizzas and quality is very good recommend any of pizza
Laatu on nyt taas sillä tasolla mitä se joskus takavuosina oli. Kiteytettynä (sisään leivottu kebab) isot annokset ja maku täydellisyyttä hipovaa, suosittelen 😃

Valitettavasti sanon, että surkean asiakaspalvelun lisäksi myös pitsojen pohjat ovat kuivia , jauhoisia ja mauttomia. Täytteitä säästellen. Kaksi kertaa olen yrittänyt saada pitzaa missä on aurajuustoa, juustoa  olen löytänyt vain suurennuslasilla. Sanovat, että voit mennä autoon odottamaan ja tuomme pitzan 5min kuluttua. Menin kysymään 10min kuluttua. Oli kuulemma uunissa. Menin takaisin autoon ja ihmettelin kun ihmisiä tulee ulos pitzalaatikoiden kanssa. Menin taas sisälle. Eivät kuulemma ehtineetkään tuomaan. Sain siis jäähtyneen pitzan ja olisin saanut odottaa autossa aamuun asti.  Terveiset terveystarkastajalle. Keittiön puolella pyörii epämääräisen paljon miehiä jotka eivät asuistaan päätellen kuulu keittiön puolelle. Kuittia ei myöskään tarjota jos maksat käteisellä. Mäkkärissäkin voit joutua hieman odottamaan ruokaa autokaistalla, mutta aina on ruoka tuotu eikä selitelty, että ei ehditty tuoda.
Ruoka ei ole kummoista ja pitkät kassajonot
Palvelu ja ruoka olivat hyvää  💖 Ruoka myös valmistui nopeasti. Hyvä ruoka, hyvä mieli. Kiitos paljon 😊

Didn't plan on stopping there, but was pleasantly surprised.
Had the Mexican Burger, ground steak hand formed, with green pepper, onion, tomato and cilantro.
Perfectly grilled from slight crust to pink center, flipped only once, I demolished it.  It was like the best home-made grilled burger I have ever made.  There's hundreds of ways to ruin a burger, but this place achieved perfection.
The traditional Mexican items were also great according to my kids.
Great selection of some Mexican classics. The price was pretty great! Wide variety of tequilas! Loved the food and the dessert! Overall very satisfied with the cozy atmosphere and service
Best red sauce for chips. My son loves the orange sauce and my parents love the green, you have to ask for it. Something for everyone. Good tacos. Staple in Glen Ellyn for many, many years.

Friendly restaurant with extensive, creative and authentic menu. They will also custom make a dish to fit your dietary needs. Fantastic margaritas...best of all the staff and owners are super people.  Have been coming here regularly for years.

Not fancy, but if you want a simple American-Mexican food with fairly standard fair for a good price, this is your place. Great for families with little kids.  If you want high end or very traditional Mexican look elsewhere. My kids love this place.

If you're looking for hearty meals, or are not used to the typical Finnish cuisine, this is definitely a great place to try out, especially for foreigners. Warm friendly staff... Food filled with flavour and spice. Quick service
Loved their pizza and place has old italian vibe to it. Definitely will go back again.
Solid experience, you can always trust this place to have good quality food

Really enjoyed the food here! Excellent flavor and great service. There is also an all you can eat salad bar. You can see from the pictures that the food looks delicious. I assure you it tastes that way as well!

Please give me a thumbs up "like" for this review... Thanks!
Quick and friendly and very tasty, despite people practically queueing to get in!
